# Rust / Cargo
# NOTE: no bare `debug` rule here — as a pattern with no slash it matches
# any path named `debug` at any depth, which silently excluded vendored
# source (warpui_core/src/debug/) and broke the CI build. Cargo build
# output lives under target/ (below), which already covers target/debug.
target
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb
**/mutants.out*/

# Node / frontend
node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Tauri
src-tauri/target
src-tauri/gen
# Bundled sidecar binaries (downloaded by scripts/download-rg.sh on
# first build) — kept out of git so the repo stays small.
src-tauri/binaries

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
*.log
logs

# Secrets — never commit
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Certificates / private keys (any format, anywhere in the tree)
*.p12
*.pfx
*.pem
*.cer
*.crt
*.key
# Common secret directories
secrets/
**/secrets/
GLI_secrets/

# RLI runtime data (per-project worktrees, local DB, etc.)
.rli/
